ad.title: Garde d'enfant/Ménage
ad.content:
Hello!

My name is Charmaine, 31 years old from the Philippines. 

I am currently a nanny and a housekeeper working 39 hours(declared) per week for a family in 17th arrondissement. I take care of children ages 6 and 9. I also had a previous experience taking care of a 4 year old little girl. I started my nanny job last March 2022 so overall I have 18 months working experience(and still counting). 

My job consists of :
With Children:
- picking up the children from school and taking them to different activities. If the weather permits, we go to parks too. 
- Giving goûter and preparing simple dinner(mostly cutting veggies, making salad and frying).
- Playing with them(board games, puzzles, drawing and coloring).
- Supervising them when showering.
- Night babysitting from time to time.
Housekeeping:
  - Cleaning the whole house(vacuum&mop)
  - Laundry and Ironing( I fold and iron well)
  - Changing bedsheets once a week.
  - Cleaning windows, oven and refrigerator once a month( if given enough time and mostly when the family is in vacation)

I am a very tidy person, calm and gentle with kids. I can speak  English almost fluently( I say almost because I am not a native speaker) and I can understand/speak A2 level in French. I also don't do 1 month vacation straight and always try my best to adapt to the schedule of the family I work with. I do bring my own food as I do not want my employer to worry about this. 

I am seeking lesser hours, around 20 hours and maximum of 35 hours per week. I can also do several part times depending on the employers area. If you needed lesser than 20 hours then we can discuss about it. 

I wanted a long term position if possible. 

I live in Saint Ouen. I am near metro 14, RER C and metro 13. I do not have any problem travelling within Paris.

Non plus sérieusement, je suis une femme très ordonnée, très professionnel, à l'écoute de vos besoins, et j'ai toujours tendance à en faire plus que ce qu'il faudrait.
